1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to revenue and taxation; to eliminate an
2 income reduction for extraordinary dividends and certain capital
3 gains; to provide an operative date; and to outright repeal sections
4 77-2715.08 and 77-2715.09, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska.
5 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
